{"tid":2385962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"telegram 教人將whatsapp chat record搬去tg","createTime":"2021-01-29T09:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T17:18:17.000Z","uid":213446,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7be84f05142dcf52150e47e351954c0adc7a266a","tid":2385962,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T09:49:29.000Z","msg":"telegram 萬歲<br />\n<br />\nMove Chat History from Other Apps<br />\n&bull; Move your message history from other apps such as WhatsApp and KakaoTalk to Telegram.<br />\n&bull; Use the Export Chat function in the other app, then Share the exported file to Telegram (see blog post for detailed instructions).<br />\n<br />\nMore Privacy<br />\n&bull; Delete not only messages, but also groups you created, secret chats, and call history for all sides, without a trace.<br />\n<br />\nImproved Voice Chats<br />\n&bull; Adjust volume for individual participants of a voice chat.<br />\n&bull; See active voice chats from your groups at the top of the Call History section.<br />\n<br />\nImproved Music Player<br />\n&bull; Tap the artist name in the music player to see tracks by that artist from all your chats.<br />\n&bull; Pause and resume songs with a fade effect.<br />\n&bull; Press and hold the &lsquo;Next&rsquo; and &lsquo;Previous&rsquo; buttons to fast-forward or rewind the track.<br />\n<br />\nAnd More<br />\n&bull; Greet new users in one tap with a suggested sticker.<br />\n&bull; Enjoy improved TalkBack support.<br />\n&bull; Report fake groups or channels impersonating famous people or organizations by opening their Profile &gt; ⋮ &gt; Report.<br />\n<br />\nMore about this update:<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.org/blog/move-history\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fblog%2Fmove-history&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=d0390543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.org/blog/move-history</a>"},{"pid":"234756